![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1577212142284-GLJEJ457SW8HJQ7695FZ/image-asset.jpeg)

What makes a good superhero movie? Well, Teen Titans Go To The Movies checks all those boxes and more. Excitement? Check. Laughs? Check? Upbeat inspiration songs about life? Double Check. Listen to the guys of ComicBook Clique review a film based on a tv show noone wanted, and see how this feature film is changing peoples minds when it comes to the Teen Titans. Crack an egg on it!

If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
Send us feedback at **ComicBookClique@Gmail.com!** You Are Worthy! 

